'''''Out Of This Gloomy Light''''' is the 2003 Demo from [[Swallow the Sun]]. Recorded at Sam's Workshop January 2003. Recorded, engineered and mixed by Sami Kokko. Produced by Swallow the Sun. Composed by J. Raivio. Arranged by Swallow
the Sun.

